    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "62003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>我們如何知道何為愛？</strong></p><p>因為基督為我們捨棄了祂的生命，我們就知道何為愛。</p>",
