    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "62004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>你如何知道神的靈？</strong></p><p>凡承認耶穌基督是道成肉身的靈，就是出於神。</p>",
