    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "62004009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>神如何向我們顯明祂的愛？  </strong></p><p>神差遣祂的獨生子到世上，藉此向我們顯明祂的愛。</p>",
